# ! Under construction ! Deployed for testing purposes
- App is working but has following limitations: 
	- No media queries yet. Display is optimized only for mobile view (vertical). 
	- Not optimized
	- Refactoring of code is still in progress
	 
## Specs
Built with React HOOKS, 

3rd party used: 
- Moment 
- Tippy
	
This project was bootstrapped with [Create React App](https://github.com/facebook/create-react-app).

## Weather App
Displays weather data from *OpenWeather* API. 

#### App functionalities
- searching for a city
- save a city for fast access (up to 3 cities) in local storage
- set a city to load at startup
- validation of input & error handling 


